features: SELF FEEDING SET: BLW E-book | 17-piece baby feeding set contains 1 x baby suction plate, 1 x suction plate lid, 1 x suction bowl, 1 x wooden fork, 1 x wooden spoon, 1 x sippy cup, 1 x sippy cup straw, 1 x sippy cup lid, 1 x baby bib with catcher, 1 x first stage toddler fork, 1 x first stage toddler spoon, 1 x steel spoon, 1 x steel fork, 1 x fruit feeder, 1 x fruit juicer cap, 1 x finger toothbrush, and 1 x toothbrush cover.
Material and Quality: Crafted from food-grade silicone, our feeding set is free from BPA, PVC, and phthalates. Durable and safe, it withstands daily use while maintaining its pristine condition.

Design with Care - Spoons & Fork: Our wooden spoons and forks are crafted to be soft and gentle for your baby. The back of small silicone cutlery features sensory bumps, providing a playful texture that aids in sensory development. Thoughtfully sized for little hands, these utensils ensure easy grasping and comfortable holding, turning every meal into a delightful experience for your child. They are safe and eco-friendly.

Consistently Strong Suction: Our suction plate and bowl have been rigorously tested for strong suction. The large suction base ensures plates and bowls stay securely in place until mealtime is over, promoting your child's independence in self-feeding without messy accidents. Designed for ultimate stability, our suction power outperforms smaller suctions.

Invest in a Long-Lasting Toddler Tableware Set: Every piece in our set is dishwasher safe and easy to clean with soap and warm water. Safe for use in the microwave or refrigerator, our set is designed for long-lasting durability.
Thoughtful Gift: Our vibrant and neutral color feeding set is the perfect gift for expecting moms, making it an ideal choice for baby showers and birthdays.
